---
import "../styles/global.css"
---

<style>
	nav a:focus, nav a:hover {
		color: var(--color-theme-cream);
	}
</style>

<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<!-- <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" /> -->
		<meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
		<meta name="robots" content="noindex, nofollow">
		 <!-- This site uses Tailwind. Ignore the linked stylesheet. 
		To follow, look at the classes and reference https://tailwindcss.com/ -->
		<noscript><style> .jsonly { display: none } </style></noscript>
		<title>Addie Bart - Home</title>
	</head>

    <body class="bg-theme-pink box-border p-4 ">

		<p class="bg-theme-green box-border px-2 max-w-4/5 w-fit mx-auto font-['Minecraft']">
			This new website is still under construction.
			Expect more to show up soon!
			Sorry mobile users.
		</p>
        
		<div class="flex flex-row max-w-4/5 w-280 p-4 h-fit border-4 border-dashed my-5 box-border gap-x-4 relative self-center-safe">

			<img src="/img/Scissors_icon_black.svg" alt="A scissors icon, purely for aesthetics." class="w-10 absolute right-0 top-8 translate-x-1/2 rotate-90 jsonly">

			<nav class="flex flex-col max-w-2/5 min-w-40 w-1/5 border box-border p-2 bg-theme-purple text-md font-['Minecraft'] text-center gap-y-4">
				<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">Links, ig</h2>
				<ul class="flex flex-col gap-y-2">
					<li>
						<a href="/">Back to landing</a>
					</li>
					<li>
						<a href="/old ">Old Website</a>
					</li>
					<li>
						That's the end of the links.
						<div class="text-3xl">:(</div>
					</li>
				</ul>
			</nav>

			<main class="grow bg-[url(/img/notebooktile.png)] p-8 font-['Minecraft'] gap-y-4 flex flex-col box-content relative">

				<h1 class="mx-auto w-fit text-4xl underline -underline-offset-10 italic block decoration-4 font-['Minecraftia']">
					Welcome To My WebZone!
				</h1>

				<article class="mt-4 text-xl flex flex-col gap-y-8">
					<div class="flex flex-row">
						<img src="/img/amandaprofile.png" width="500" height="500" alt="A pseudo-profile picture of Amanda O'Neil for the anime 'Little Witch Acedemia'." class="w-60 max-w-1/3 h-fit mr-6 border-2">
						<div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
							<h2 class="text-3xl">
								My name is
								<span id="name" class="font-semibold">Addie!</span>
							</h2>
							<p>
								I'm a tech enthusiast and software/systems engineer.
							</p>
							<p>
								I'm about to graduate from the University of Kansas and start
								a technical internship with a tax preparation company.
							</p>
							<p>
								Outside of computer science and software engineering,
								I enjoy board games, anime, recreational cycling, and
								<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Construction_and_management_simulation" target="_blank" class="underline hover:text-theme-green">
									management simulation video games
								</a>.
							</p>
						</div>
						
					</div>

					<p>
						My primary software interest areas are in full-stack web development and writing secure software.
						To this end, my favorite language is TypeScript - primarily for its wide use in the web domain,
						expansive package ecosystem,
						its expressive yet strict typing system, and its emphasis on static analysis.
						That said, I also enjoy writing in other languages including C++, C#, and Java.
					</p>

					<p>
						This website is intended as place for everything me!
						You should see a list of links on the sidebar - I encourage you to explore them.
						Right now, there might not be a whole lot there, but I plan to add sections as they become pertinent.
						My previous website had been around since I was in middle school and was in dire need of replacement.
						Hopefully, this site fares better and stands the test of time.
					</p>

					<p>
						Hope you enjoy your stay here!
					</p>
				</article>

				<img src="/img/markerstar.png" alt="A star, hand-drawn with marker" class="jsonly absolute right-2 top-3 w-20 rotate-9">

			</main>

		</div>

		<div class="grow"></div>

		<div class="flex">
			<p class="text-md p-2 bg-theme-purple border w-fit font-['Minecraft'] h-fit self-end">
				This site was made with &lt;3 using human hands.
			</p>
			<div class="grow"></div>
